Usage: quill compile [flags] <template-name>

Flags:
  -autoescape string
    	output escaping strategy: "off" (default, source emission) or "html" (default "off")
  -func string
    	name of the generated render function (default "Render")
  -o string
    	output file for the generated source; default stdout
  -pkg string
    	package clause of the generated file (default "qtpl")
  -root string
    	template root directory the loader resolves names under (default ".")
  -seed int
    	fixed seed for the randomness callables; omit the flag for the time-seeded default
  -strict
    	strict-undefined handling; -strict=false compiles the lenient migration mode (default true)
  -tabwidth int
    	spaces one indent level expands to (the WithTabWidth knob) (default 4)
